"title": "6634: deliverance",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6634",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God frequently rescues people from danger, suffering and sin, often through human agency.</p>\n<h2>The source of deliverance</h2>\n<h3>Deliverance comes from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:8\">PSA 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:7-Exod3:8\">EXO 3:7–3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:16-Dan3:17\">DAN 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:9\">JON 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>There is no deliverance by other gods</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:33\">2KI 18:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:18\">ISA 36:18</a></p>\n<h3>There is no escape from God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:13\">ISA 43:13</a></p>\n<h3>Deliverance may be declined</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:53-Matt26:54\">MAT 26:53–26:54</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:36\">JHN 18:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:35\">HEB 11:35</a></p>\n<h2>Different kinds of deliverance</h2>\n<h3>From danger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:37\">1SA 17:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:23-Luke8:24\">LUK 8:23–8:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:9-2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:17\">2TI 4:17</a></p>\n<h3>From illness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:3\">PSA 103:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:16\">ISA 38:16</a></p>\n<h3>From trouble</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:17\">PSA 34:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:19\">PSA 34:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps54:7\">PSA 54:7</a></p>\n<h3>From slavery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:2\">EXO 20:2</a></p>\n<h3>From enemies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:10-Jer38:13\">JER 38:10–38:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:19-Dan6:22\">DAN 6:19–6:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:74\">LUK 1:74</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:2\">2TH 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>From Satan</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:31-Luke22:32\">LUK 22:31–22:32</a></p>\n<h3>From the fear of death</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14-Heb2:15\">HEB 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>From all fears</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:4\">PSA 34:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:17\">REV 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>From sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:4\">GAL 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:7\">PSA 32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>From the coming wrath</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:7\">LUK 3:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:9\">1TH 5:9</a></p>\n<h2>Deliverance for God's people</h2>\n<h3>God promises deliverance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:11\">JER 15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:1\">DAN 12:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's people are to pray for deliverance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:19\">2KI 19:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:20\">ISA 37:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:1-Ps59:2\">PSA 59:1–59:2</a></p>\n<h2>The means of deliverance</h2>\n<h3>Direct intervention by God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:13\">EXO 14:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:6\">2KI 7:6</a></p>\n<h3>Deliverance by angels</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:7\">ACT 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Deliverance by human agency</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:17-Gen37:22\">GEN 37:17–37:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:16\">JDG 2:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:16-Acts23:24\">ACT 23:16–23:24</a></p>\n<h2>God's people as deliverers</h2>\n<h3>Abraham</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:14-Gen14:16\">GEN 14:14–14:16</a></p>\n<h3>Moses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:35-Acts7:36\">ACT 7:35–7:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:20\">PSA 77:20</a></p>\n<h3>Joshua</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:8-Exod17:13\">EXO 17:8–17:13</a></p>\n<h3>The judges</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:16\">JDG 2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:9\">JDG 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:15\">JDG 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:31\">JDG 3:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:1-Judg4:10\">JDG 4:1–4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:23\">JDG 4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:12\">JDG 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:16\">JDG 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:1\">JDG 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:32\">JDG 11:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:2-Judg13:5\">JDG 13:2–13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:24-Judg13:25\">JDG 13:24–13:25</a></p>\n<h3>Samuel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:3-1Sam7:13\">1SA 7:3–7:13</a></p>\n<h3>Saul</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:9-1Sam11:13\">1SA 11:9–11:13</a></p>\n<h3>Jonathan</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:45\">1SA 14:45</a></p>\n<h3>David</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:1\">2SA 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:14\">2SA 8:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:18–4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5\">1TI 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14-Heb2:15\">HEB 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Ministers and others through the gospel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:17-Acts26:18\">ACT 26:17–26:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:25-2Tim2:26\">2TI 2:25–2:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:19-Jas5:20\">JAS 5:19–5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Gifted Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:1\">MAT 10:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1\">LUK 9:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:17\">MRK 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:6\">ACT 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:6-Acts8:7\">ACT 8:6–8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:16-Acts16:18\">ACT 16:16–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:10\">1CO 12:10</a></p>\n<h2>The proper response to deliverance</h2>\n<h3>Praise</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:25\">LUK 5:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:8\">ACT 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Delight</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1\">1SA 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>Thanksgiving</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:11-Ps30:12\">PSA 30:11–30:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:47\">PSA 106:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:6-Ps107:8\">PSA 107:6–107:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:14-Ps107:15\">PSA 107:14–107:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:20-Ps107:21\">PSA 107:20–107:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:30-Ps107:31\">PSA 107:30–107:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:24-Rom7:25\">ROM 7:24–7:25</a></p>\n<h3>Trust</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:1-Ps40:3\">PSA 40:1–40:3</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:12-Ps56:13\">PSA 56:12–56:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:38-Luke8:39\">LUK 8:38–8:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:14\">JHN 5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:10-John8:11\">JHN 8:10–8:11</a></p>",
